<p>The only market available for Index Options is <code>Market.USA</code>. You don't need to pass a <code class="csharp">Market</code><code class="python">market</code> argument to the <code class="csharp">AddIndexOptionContract</code><code class="python">add_index_option_contract</code> method because the contract <code>Symbol</code> already contains the market.</p>